- [ ] NetworkConditions for various scenarios
- [ ] Fault injection (partition, delay, loss)
- [ ] DistributedLabRuntime coordinating nodes
- [ ] Deterministic execution with seed
- [ ] Distributed trace capture
- [ ] Test pattern examples
